cdata.name: Big Data Block
cdata.desc:
Big Data Block is a Big Data (large volume of data) analysis platform. It provides the users with A.I-based tools to make a structured data treatment in order to optimize the Big Data usage within their projects. In addition, Big Data Block enables the access to a marketplace to match the platform users with technical support experts.

The BDB token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency. It is a utility token, it will power the Big Data Block platform, and serve as a medium of reward miners.
